<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Code generation</b></p><p>IntelliJ IDEA can generate getter and setter methods for fields in your class. With the caret inside the class, press <span class="shortcut">&shortcut:Generate;</span> (<span class="control">Code | Generate</span>).</p><p class="image"><img src="images/ij_tips_generate_getter_setter.png" alt="Generate getter and setter" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>